pd_1_com_2text: Do you remember how well we had together?
pd_5_com_0text: Sure, see you there in half an hour.
pd_7_com_0text: Alright Rosita, but after that, you give me the booze.
pd_9_com_0text: What did you do before you came here?
pd_9_com_1text: Were you a gang? How many you were? And who are they?
pd_9_com_2text: Do you remember to kill a couple; twelve years ago; two days south walking from here?
pd_10_com_0text: Well I was a criminal, a fine criminal.
pd_11_com_0text: We were four but I can't tell you who. Why you ask me those things?
pd_12_com_0text: Ehmm.. yeah I remember a couple in house in the woods not too far from here, so what?
pd_13_com_0text: That's all. Here, grab the bottle.
